1. *Strašno* je što se ovo desilo. (It's terrible that this happened.)
2. Ono što je nastalo je bilo *strašno*. (What emerged was terrible.)
3. Ova situacija je *strašna*. (This situation is terrible.)
4. Ljudi su bili *strašno* zaprepašćeni. (People were terribly shocked.)
5. To je bilo *strašno*. (That was terrible.)
6. Oni su bili *strašno* uznemireni. (They were terribly disturbed.)